Description: Browser 2030B — privacy-first, default-deny web browser
 A memory-safe, post-quantum-ready browser. Telemetry, network egress, AI
 features, and site permissions are all default-deny and opt-in. Built from a
 single monorepo with Rust engine components and a Tauri/TypeScript shell.
